{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"59435cd3b1","title":"关于同意曾养甫、陈立夫所提四条并派潘汉年为正式代表致刘鼎电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"43dbe9b778","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"59435cd3b1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76fab124dd","type":"paragraph","text":"关于同意曾养甫、陈立夫所提四条并派潘汉年为正式代表致刘鼎电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"f083059a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月12日）刘：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"85a34e33ad","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、宁夏计划蒋介石正积极破坏中，我方正想对策，请毅“办为我筹之。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"b629654197","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、借毅之款五个月后可交还，但目前尚需五万元应急，毅处还可设法否。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"b91abd751d","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、张子华已到，对曾养甫、陈立夫所提之：（一）共产党公开活动。（二）苏维埃继续存在。（三）苏区派代表参加国会。（四）及红军改名，照国民革命军编制及待遇，但不变更原有人员等四条，我方均可同意，并派汉年为正式代表，迅速进行谈判，请告毅知之。要毅多方设法促其早成，并告卢伟良面告汉年，速按此方针谈判。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"a4dcc37f96","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、十六团人马已交还类。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"cce5ad5f8b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"},{"id":"9de0b50445","type":"paragraph","text":"文玄[11指张学良。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1"}],"page":{"id":"5d2c67cb24","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"59435cd3b1","start":292,"end":292}}}},